L2_gloss: The first letter of the Nuer alphabet, written in the Latin script.
third-person singular pronoun in the nominative case; he, she, it

are (plural of be)
Kɛ kɛn cak.There are the milks.

am, are, is (plural of be)
Nɛmɛ ɛ yaŋ.This is cow.
First-person singular pronoun in the nominative case; I
